#: ../../splunkplatform/practice-reliability/incident-response.rst:40
msgid "Splunk Observability Cloud components all contribute to the data analytics in Splunk Observability Cloud dashboards. You can see charts and dashboards in APM, Infrastructure Monitoring, and RUM. You can also go to the homepage for all Splunk Observability Cloud dashboards to see dashboards and charts created in each component, including log views or logs data displayed in a chart."
