#: ../../splunkplatform/practice-reliability/incident-response.rst:52
msgid "APM collects traces and spans to monitor your distributed applications. You can investigate the root cause of an error with the service map or find the root cause of an error using Tag Spotlight. To learn how, see :ref:`service-map` and :ref:`troubleshoot-tag-spotlight`. For more examples of APM troubleshooting scenarios, see :ref:`apm-scenarios-intro`."
